# Findings that are intentional for this disposable test environment.
# Each is accepted on purpose for the reason given.

# Webserver and ProxySQL need outbound 80/443/53 to reach public package
# mirrors and to download Adminer. There's no NAT gateway in this single-VPC
# demo, so that egress is to 0.0.0.0/0 on those ports by design.
AVD-AWS-0104

# RDS deletion protection is left off so the environment tears down cleanly
# (see #18) — this is a throwaway stack, not production.
AVD-AWS-0177

# Performance Insights is left off to keep the demo on free micro instances.
AVD-AWS-0133

# The toolchain image is an interactive CLI that bind-mounts the host repo,
# so it runs as root to match the host user's files.
AVD-DS-0002

# The toolchain image is a CLI, not a long-running service, so it has no
# HEALTHCHECK.
AVD-DS-0026
